column5: just got back from the states. 300yds for $29. i pay 48 here.
I pay $30 for 300 yds of 65 lb. @ Cabelas.
I bought 1500 yards of 80 for $63 last year and 1500yds of 30 for $45. Ebay !
yup... ebay is the way to go..
Even here you can get 300 yards of 50 pound and under for under $30...just gotta shop around.
for me to shop around i have to spend 60 in gas
